OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F155A1777206670
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/4
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSC5 to close satellite SD service on
OL,4,CThursday
OL,5,
OL,6,F5 will shut down the standard
OL,7,Fdefinition version of its main channel
OL,8,Fon satellite this Thursday, drawing a
OL,9,Fnear-complete end to SD broadcasting
OL,10,Famong the UK's PSB broadcasters on the
OL,11,Fplatform (excluding + 1 SD services).
OL,13,FThe move follows similar transitions by
OL,14,Fthe BBC in early 2024, ITV during 2023
OL,15,Fand 2024, and Channel 4 in late 2024.
OL,23,EPub: 03-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,156,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15502
SC,0002
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F155A1777206670
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSC5 to close satellite SD service on
OL,4,CThursday
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe change has little practical impact
OL,7,Fon viewers. A 2024 estimate by ITV put
OL,8,Fthe number of SD-reliant homes at fewer
OL,9,Fthan 1%. A figure that will have
OL,10,Fdwindled further following technical
OL,11,Fchanges to Sky's platform that rendered
OL,12,Fits earliest receivers obsolete.
OL,14,F5's offshoot channels ` 5USA, 5Star,
OL,15,F5Action and 5Select ` remain SD-only on
OL,16,Fsatellite, with HD access confined to
OL,17,Finternet-based offerings such as 5's
OL,18,Fon-demand service and Sky Stream.
OL,20,FTwo public service broadcasters retain
OL,21,FSD satellite feeds: STV and S4C.
OL,23,EPub: 03-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,156,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15503
SC,0003
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F155A1777206670
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/4
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSC5 to close satellite SD service on
OL,4,CThursday
OL,5,
OL,6,FTwo variants of STV (for Dundee and
OL,7,FEdinburgh) are available in SD only.
OL,8,FThis is believed to be a means of
OL,9,Favoiding the cost of broadcasting these
OL,10,Fvariants on expensive pan-European
OL,11,Fsatellite capacity that would require
OL,12,Fencryption.
OL,14,FAs part of a recent review of the
OL,15,Ffuture of TV distribution by Ofcom, S4C
OL,16,Fargued that the costs of maintaining a
OL,17,Fpresence on Digital Terrestrial TV
OL,18,F(Freeview) and satellite platforms are
OL,19,Fsubstantial and represent a significant
OL,20,Fongoing financial commitment for the
OL,21,Fbroadcaster, and eat into the content
OL,22,Fbudget.
OL,23,EPub: 03-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,156,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15504
SC,0004
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F155A1777206670
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/4
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSC5 to close satellite SD service on
OL,4,CThursday
OL,5,
OL,6,FWorth noting that the STV and S4C SD
OL,7,Fservices use the DVB-S2 standard which
OL,8,Flegacy SD-only receivers don't support.
OL,23,EPub: 03-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
